This issue is a follow-up to the earlier discussion in #33682.

That previous issue was closed because I was not able to narrow down the cause clearly enough at the time. After more testing, I now have a more specific and much smaller observation, so I am reopening the discussion in a more focused form.

The narrower behavior I am seeing is related to `receiveShadow` on the WebGPU path.

After removing and disposing a glTF model, the observed Heap Snapshot behavior changes depending on whether there is still another object in the scene with 

